REGGANG
PASTA ENTREE
PARMESAN CHEESE
Angel Hair Pasta with Naturally Flavored
Parmesan Cheese Sauce Mix
YOU WILL NEED
s cups
hot water
h cup
milk
2 tablespoons
margarine or butter
STOVE TOP
MICROWAVE
I In medium saucepan, bring 1% cups water, h
cup milk and 2 tablespoons margarine or
butter to a boil.
I In 2-quart microwavable dish, combine I
cups water, cup milk and 2 tablespoons
margarine or butter. Stir Microwave
uncovered on HIGH (100%) 4-5 minutes
or until boiling.
2 Slowly stir in pasta and seasoning. Separate
pasta with a fork, if needed. Return to a boil,
stirring occasionally. Reduce heat to
MEDIUM. Boil uncovered, 4-5 minutes until
pasta is just tender, stirring frequently.
2 Slowly stir in pasta and seasoning
Microwave on HIGH I minutes. Stir
3 Microwave on HIGH 3-4 minutes more.
Sauce will be thin. Let stand 3-5 minutes
to thicken.
3 Sauce will be thin. Let stand 3-5 minutes for
sauce to thicken. Do not overcook.
Microwave ovens vary, adjust times as needed.
STIR IN OR TOPPING IDEAS:
Prepare as directed above for Stove Top, then stir in
the following in Step 3:
• I cup cherry tomato halves
